中，车主和特斯拉均不能远程在线查看。 另外，特斯拉公司已在中国建立数据中心，以实现数据存储的本地化。所有在中国大陆市场销售车辆所产生的数据，都会存储在中国境内。2021 年 10 月政府主管部门联合发布《汽车数据安全管理若干规定（试行）》后，特斯拉公司作为首批试点企业，积极参与了主管部门组织的合规试点工作。 非常感谢网友们的关心，让我们一起加速世界向可持续能源的转变。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-1a188a917f06bdd6e5f79b2ccfb2eaec_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "68 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/617236443"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIurrH3bXqlNFeEAMaCDk5NDQzNzE5IISM6KYGMAA4rwJAD3IJNjE3MjM2NDQzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1692076035.594369", "card_id": "Q_617252207", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 32}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "当电动汽车充电和加油一样快，电动汽车会完全取代燃油车吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "在当下的汽车制造行业水平条件下，电动汽车和燃油汽车各有优缺点，两种汽车都有相当一部分的用户。 电动汽车充电慢是一个大问题，假设现在电动汽车充满电和燃油汽车加满油一样，就是两三分钟的事，其他所有现有条件不变，但允许汽车行业在此基础上发展。 不出几年，电动汽车会完全取代燃油汽车吗？欢迎各位答主说说自己的想法。"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "67 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/617252207"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IurrH3bXqlNFeEAMaCDk5NDQ3MjIyIMyq6KYGMAA4JkAQcgk2MTcyNTIyMDd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1692076035.594927", "card_id": "Q_617208511", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count"